Come back to you, friends

208
00:23:04,430 --> 00:23:08,270
Come back to you, friends
Come back to you, friends

209
00:23:08,270 --> 00:23:10,970
Come back to you, friends

210
00:23:25,140 --> 00:23:28,250
Hey, you stupid bird!
Where're you taking me?!

211
00:23:28,250 --> 00:23:31,330
What's with this cave?! Where's the exit?!

212
00:23:31,330 --> 00:23:34,150
Yikes! The giant snake!
It seems irritable for some reason!

213
00:23:34,150 --> 00:23:37,670
Aah! Why is this snake coming after us?!

214
00:23:37,670 --> 00:23:41,090
Huh? Looks like we got us
some ferocious ones here...

215
00:23:41,090 --> 00:23:42,340
On the next episode of One Piece!

216
00:23:42,340 --> 00:23:46,120
"0% Survival Rate! Chopper vs. Ohm,
the Sword Wielding Priest"

217
00:23:46,120 --> 00:23:48,180
I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
